Package me.marcosassuncao.servsim.job

Class DefaultWorkUnit

java.lang.Object
me.marcosassuncao.servsim.job.DefaultWorkUnit
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<DefaultWorkUnit>, WorkUnit
Direct Known Subclasses:
Job, Reservation
public class DefaultWorkUnit extends Object implements WorkUnit, Comparable<DefaultWorkUnit>
This class represents a simple work unit to be processed by a server entity. It's an implementation of DefaultWorkUnit
Author:
Marcos Dias de Assuncao
